10 Hair Products for Thicker Hair


July 26, 2017July 26, 2017
Hair, Shampoo/Conditioner
by Chanchala Bose








 




 




 




Hi IMBBians, 
There is a set of hair care products that you need in your daily life in order to make your hair healthier and thicker. Let’s have a look at some of the best hair products for thicker hair.








Matrix Opti Care Smoothing Conditioner

Thick hair is mostly unmanageable. Thus, you need a smoothening effect the most. When your thick hair is well polished it will look great. And, this is what this conditioner from Matrix does. It is enriched with shea butter, which helps in conditioning and managing your hair. It gives a beautiful shine to your hair and makes it thicker. 




L’Oreal Professionnel X-Tenso Care Nutri-Reconstructor Shampoo
This professional shampoo from the house of L’Oreal is known to keep excess oil at bay. Thick hair suffers the issue of excessive oil and dirt, thus your scalp is more prone to infections. The botanical extracts and amino acids in this shampoo cleanse your hair well and infuse new life into it. 
Organix Renewing Moroccan Argan Oil Conditioner

The conditioner is enriched with the magical argan oil. Argan oil is known to condition your hair and take care of the dry tresses. This conditioner strengthens the roots, thus considerably reducing hair breakage and increasing volume. This conditioner penetrates well and provides full nourishment to your hair. 




L’Oreal Hair Spa Detoxifying Conditioner
This is a detoxifying conditioner which detangles your hair, giving it a smooth and balanced look. The professional range acts as a spa for your hair. The conditioner is enriched with multiple magical oils, which are known to revamp your hair and giving it a salon-like finish. 
Toni and Guy Smooth Definition Shampoo For Dry Hair







This shampoo gives a new look and definition to your hair. It penetrates into each and every hair strand, thus makes them soft and voluminous. This shampoo is specifically meant for dry hair and it gives your dry and damaged hair the right kind of nourishment. Regular usage of this shampoo makes your hair healthier and thicker.
BBlunt Perfect Balance Shampoo for Normal to Dry Hair
This one makes sure that the pH level of your hair is well-maintained. Hence, your hair remains protected from issues like infections, hair loss etc, which eventually leads to thicker hair.




L’Oreal Professionnel Sensi Balance Soothing Shampoo

Thick hair or voluminous hair needs to be cleansed very well. This shampoo has a gentle cleansing formula which cleanses the roots of your hair effectively. Also, the shampoo is enriched with sorbitan technology, which is known to take care of your tresses. Overall, this shampoo keeps your hair healthy and give it a new life. 
Wella Luxe Oil
The serum is lightweight but silky in consistency. It smells amazing, too! This Wella serum is enriched with many luxurious oils and it gives a smooth feel to your hair. It is also embedded with Keratin protection which keeps your hair protected while treating it well. 






Innisfree Camellia Essential Hair Oil Serum

The serum is enriched with Jeju camellia oil and fermented camellia oil which make a double coating of protection layer for the hair. This serum prevents damage, seals in moisture and treats damaged hair well. The serum is very lightweight and gives your hair a healthier, thicker appearance. 
Moroccanoil Treatment Light
This is a quick fix for your hair. This light treatment can be used in multiple ways. The light
treatment can be used for styling, detangling, and even to add a boost of moisture. If your hair has become lifeless and dull, you really need to try this one. 
